{
  "id": "69fedd84b928a4a1f82d7c85",
  "title": "辛いの種類ってどのくらいあるんだ",
  "created": 1778310533,
  "updated": 1778311446,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69fedd84b928a4a1f82d7c85",
      "text": "辛いの種類ってどのくらいあるんだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069694e",
      "text": "from [2026/05/09]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069694f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310536
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696950",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696951",
      "text": " [辛い]の種類ってどのくらいあるんだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310539
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696952",
      "text": " \t[つらい]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310540
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696953",
      "text": " \t[からい]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310541
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696954",
      "text": " \t\t[トウガラシ]：[カプサイシン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310544
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696955",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/76688afbdf60b9495fa868bb9f8dbaff]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696956",
      "text": "  \t\t[カプサイシン]は[アルカロイド]のうち、[カプサイシノイド]の一種",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310586
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696958",
      "text": " \t\t[からし]・[マスタード]：[アリルイソチオシアネート]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310603
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696959",
      "text": "  \t\t[https://gyazo.com/b79e7426a1de2e307d81523813ab0148]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069695a",
      "text": "  \t\t[有機硫黄化合物]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310606
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069695b",
      "text": "  \t\t[芥子油]、[アリル芥子油]とも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310612
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069695c",
      "text": " \t\t[ワサビ]：[シニグリン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310617
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069695d",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/8b94a04771df98920be711523f437118]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069695e",
      "text": "    [ブドウ糖]と[芥子油]が結合した[配糖体]（[グルコシノレート]）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310657
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069695f",
      "text": "    すりおろすなどして[酸素]と触れると、[ミロシナーゼ]の作用で[グルコース]と[硫酸水素カリウム]が遊離し、[アリルイソチオシアネート]を生じる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310697
    },
    {
      "id": "69fede4a0000000000696970",
      "text": "    [ワサビ]は辛味の中にほんのりと甘みがある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310731,
      "updated": 1778311354
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696960",
      "text": " \t\t[コショウ]：",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311351
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696961",
      "text": " \t\t\t[ピペリン]：[アルカロイド]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311348
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696962",
      "text": "  \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/2c5e61bb29a53efee8beeb95a276c22f]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696963",
      "text": "  \t\t\t[幾何異性体]に[シャビシン]がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311333
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696964",
      "text": "   \t\t\t[ピペリン]は[トランス型]、[シャビシン]は[シス型]。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311342
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696965",
      "text": " \t\t\t[シャビシン]：[アルカロイド]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311367
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696966",
      "text": "  \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/b905110cc0176369c2fe439f046252b7]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696967",
      "text": "  \t\t\t[幾何異性体]に[ピペリン]がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311376
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696968",
      "text": "   \t\t\t[シャビシン]は[シス型]、[ピペリン]は[トランス型]。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311386
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd840000000000696969",
      "text": " \t\t[塩]：[塩化ナトリウム]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311399
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069696a",
      "text": " \t\t\t[塩辛い]（しおからい）と表現される",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311402
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069696b",
      "text": " \t\t\t[辛い]（からい）と表現する地域がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311404
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069696c",
      "text": " \t総合的には[痛覚神経]が[刺激]される感覚に近いんじゃないかな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311414
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069696d",
      "text": " \t\tつらいと[痛覚神経]が刺激されるという話があった気がする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311434
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069696e",
      "text": " \t\t[カプサイシン]（[トウガラシ]の成分）は[痛覚神経]を刺激する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778311446
    },
    {
      "id": "69fedd84000000000069696f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778310533,
      "updated": 1778310533
    }
  ]
}